question:
What is the error in the following C code?

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int num = 2;
    switch (num) {
        case 1:
            printf("One");
        case 2:
            printf("Two");
        case 3:
            printf("Three");
        default:
            printf("Default");
    }
    return 0;
}
```

